---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — The Electric Bike Superstore"
  description="Learn about The Electric Bike Superstore — our mission to make e-biking accessible, our expert team, and our commitment to quality."
  type="website"
  canonicalURL={new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site).toString()}
>
  <section class="section-sm">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <div class="page-header">
        <span class="badge badge-new" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Our Story</span>
        <h1>About The <span class="gradient-text">EB Superstore</span></h1>
        <p>We're on a mission to put everyone on an electric bike. Here's why.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <p class="lead">The Electric Bike Superstore was founded on a simple belief: electric bikes aren't just a fun toy — they're the future of transportation. They reduce traffic, cut emissions, save money, and make riding accessible to everyone — regardless of age or fitness level.</p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>We're here to make buying an e-bike as easy and enjoyable as riding one. From our expert-curated bike selection to our comprehensive buying guides, we give you everything you need to find the perfect e-bike for your life.</p>

        <p>Every bike we sell is tested by our team of riders. If it doesn't meet our standards for performance, build quality, and value, it doesn't make the cut.</p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card card" style="padding: 28px;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🔋</span>
            <h3>Expert-Curated</h3>
            <p>We test every bike. Only the best models make it to our store — typically 1 in 5 bikes we evaluate.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card" style="padding: 28px;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🌍</span>
            <h3>Sustainable Transport</h3>
            <p>E-bikes produce 1/50th the CO2 of a car per mile. We're committed to greener cities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card" style="padding: 28px;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">⚡</span>
            <h3>Rider First</h3>
            <p>30-day test rides, 2-year warranties, and US-based support. Your confidence matters.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card card" style="padding: 28px;">
            <span style="font-size: 2rem;">🤝</span>
            <h3>Building Community</h3>
            <p>25,000+ riders strong. Group rides, forums, and events — e-biking is better together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Why E-Bikes?</h2>
        <p>The average American spends over $10,000 per year on car-related expenses. An e-bike costs pennies per charge, requires minimal maintenance, and — here's the kicker — often gets you across town faster than a car when you factor in parking and traffic.</p>

        <p>Plus, with pedal assist, you arrive at work without needing a shower. You get exercise on your terms. You skip the gym membership. And honestly? It's just really, really fun.</p>

        <blockquote>
          <p>"The e-bike is the most efficient vehicle on Earth — more efficient than walking, cycling, or any car."</p>
          <cite>— Energy Efficiency Research, Stanford University</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>We're a team of cyclists, engineers, and e-bike enthusiasts based in Portland, Oregon — the cycling capital of America. Between us, we've logged over 100,000 miles on electric bikes across every terrain and condition imaginable. When you call us, you're talking to someone who actually rides.</p>

        <h2>Join the Ride</h2>
        <p>Whether you're commuting, mountain biking, hauling kids, or just cruising on weekends — there's an e-bike with your name on it. Browse our store, read our guides, and join 25,000+ riders who've already made the switch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-header p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34d399, var(--color-accent)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }

  .prose { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .prose :global(.lead) { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .prose :global(h2) { color: var(--color-text-primary); margin: 48px 0 20px; font-size: 1.8rem; }
  .prose :global(p) { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .prose :global(blockquote) { border-left: 3px solid #34d399; padding: 24px 32px; margin: 40px 0; background: var(--color-bg-card); border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0; }
  .prose :global(blockquote p) { font-style: italic; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-primary); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .prose :global(blockquote cite) { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-style: normal; }

  .values-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin: 32px 0 48px; }
  .value-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 12px 0 8px; }
  .value-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
</style>
